545D625C1D1746\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> <span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile28.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F244E5B36545D625D1D33D0\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p>\n <div>\n  <br>\n </div>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify; clear: none; float: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">육수가 준비되면,</span></p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify; clear: none; float: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">반죽을 밀어줍니다. 맨처음은 넓다랗게 펴주다가 밀대에 말아감아 앞뒤로 밀어줍니다.&nbsp;</span></p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify; clear: none; float: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">이때, 덧가루 잘 뿌려주시면서 하시면 됩니다.&nbsp;</span></p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify; clear: none; float: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">반죽이 말랑하게 되어서리 잘 밀렸습니다. 그대신 덧가루를 넉넉하게 뿌렸습니다. ㅎ</span></p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify; clear: none; float: none;\"><br></p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile30.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F274B583B545D618710E46C\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> <span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile2.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2356EF3B545D61870670B0\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> <span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile10.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2150C83B545D61880BF29A\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p>\n <div>\n  <br>\n </div>\n <div>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">잘 반죽이 밀렸으면, 돌돌 말아 칼로 썰어줍니다. 탈탈 털어서 흩트러놓습니다.&nbsp;</span>\n </div>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p>\n <p style=\"text-align: justify; clear: none; float: none;\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://i1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile8.uf.tistory.com%2